Dear Leroro and Quant,

I'm very tired. I would say that I've done my best but I don't think I've done enough. It's a hard pill to swallow; to know that I've only done a fraction of what I can.

I wish I could be better. I wish I could do more for you.

I wish I could write again

I suppose that's LeroQuant to me.
